# Introduction

This API is documented in OpenAPI format and represent SAR-CWS API.

[ More introduction text goes here ]

### Notes

Use plurals for `Species/Documents/Permits/Consultations` filter names. For example, `Permits` use the following filter names: `issuingAuthorities`, `issuingYears`, and `issuingMonths`.
```json
// /api/permits/searchFilters
{
    "returnStatus": "ok",
    "order": ["issuingAuthorities", "issuingYears", "issuingMonths"],
    "filters": {
        "issuingAuthorities": [
            { "id": 2, "name": "Environment Canada" },
            { "id": 3, "name": "Department of Fisheries and Oceans" },
            { "id": 4, "name": "Parks Canada Agency" }
        ],
        "issuingYears": [
            { "id": 2000, "name": "2000" },
            { "id": 2001, "name": "2001" },
            { "id": 2002, "name": "2002" }
        ],
        "issuingMonths": [
            { "id": 0, "name": "0" },
            { "id": 1, "name": "1" },
            { "id": 2, "name": "2" }            
        ]
    }
}
```

